00:24:52.399 --> 00:24:53.638
Silakan masuk, ibu.

00:24:53.779 --> 00:24:55.484
Tapi, menantu...

00:24:55.672 --> 00:25:00.042
Dengar, kamu tidak mendengarkanku
namun memanggilku menantumu.

00:25:01.291 --> 00:25:04.331
Baiklah.  Bukan demi aku.

00:25:05.065 --> 00:25:07.104
Tapi masuk saja demi...

00:25:07.362 --> 00:25:09.327
...Wajah gembira Bondita.

00:25:18.130 --> 00:25:19.890
Masuk.

00:25:24.786 --> 00:25:27.168
Silakan masuk, ibu.

00:25:30.529 --> 00:25:33.441
Paman, dia adalah ibu Bondita.

00:25:34.740 --> 00:25:36.633
